metadata.name: Nectar 1/1
metadata.description:
Eclectic mix of upcycled apparel, off-duty 90s skate culture pieces, decopunk street styles. Miscellaneous moodboards, simulations and simulacra, through an inconspicuous hole-in-the-wall gem. Architecture, sculpture, overloads of texture clash. Ultra-bright centaurea cyanuses bunch freckled on a mango corduroy padded jacket. Mock neck contrast block black and white long sleeve shirt, boyfriend fit jeans, Medusa gray violet and silver rhinestone hair clip.

Synth Graph: a center front view portrait, 2012, photograph of a beautiful tanned female model wearing a floral yellow and blue puffy jacket with a ripped denim miniskirt, black high top sneakers, white blue hair, red lipstick, walking down Manhattan in the 2000s, highly detailed. Sampler: plms, steps: 75, scale: 11.
